node.text:
Dr. King told us, “Walk together children.” Thank you for voting, Georgia. We are all looking to you to take back the power. Show up on JAN 5 from 7am-7pm. Vote #WithLove #GAsen #Runoff @WithLoveVote

Carried by Words and Voice of Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr.
Music by @Raury
Directed by Jonathan Olinger (@jonathanolinger)
Created by HUMAN (@thehumanstory)(http://HUMAN.us)
Cinematography by Dominick Cormier, Gary Bardizbanian, Kristian Melo
Creative Direction by Sean Carasso (@SeanCarasso)
Typography by Talia Mayden (@TaliaMayden)
Executive Producer - Lilakoi Moon
Produced by Tiffany Persons (@TiffanyPersons), Becca Rogers (@seriousandmysterious)
Dr. Martin Luther, King, Jr Footage from the University of South Carolina
'Let us march on ballot boxes' speech given May 9, 1966 in Kingstree, SC

node.text:
in the words of my mama:

My Arrow in the Sky...
​​
​​For every living thing. 
​​And all that has ever lived 
​​Before us...Our Ancestors meet us at rivers edge~ 
​​As we expel, purge, and cast out the hungry ghost in the White House. 
​​Point your arrow, say your prayer and vote like hell. ​🏹​
​​
​​••••••••
​​
​​Directed by Lilakoi Moon
​​Creative Direction/Edit @danielnjohnson
​​#WithLove Creative Director @JonathanOlinger
​​
​​Produced by Tiffany Persons, Becca Rogers

Special Thanks to
Kara Walker for the contribution of her art to this film. 

Dance Cinematography 
Julia Rendleman

Dancers
Ava Holloway and Kennedy George
